content.formatted_body:
 * <p>It's a sub-heading, having a list of sections each with its own subheading kind of makes sense to me as one of the rationales:</p>
<pre><code>&lt;h1&gt;Page Heading&lt;/h1&gt;
1. &lt;h2&gt;Section Heading\&lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Stuff&lt;/p&gt;


2. &lt;h2&gt;Other section heading&lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;Stuff&lt;/p&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>Not sure about the history etc.</p>

